      <li><strong>Opener Installation & Replacement</strong> – Trusted brands like LiftMaster® Chamberlain® and Genie®</li>
      <li><strong>Preventive Maintenance Plans</strong> – So you don’t get stuck in the cold</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2 class="sub-heading">Why Central Michigan Homeowners Trust Us</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>👨‍🔧 Reliable—We keep our word, and your door moving </li>
      <li>📅 Prompt scheduling—clear communication</li>
      <li>✅ Honest recommendations—no upsells</li>
      <li>📍 Deep local roots—never subcontracted</li>
      <li>💬 5-star reviews from your neighbors</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

